DataElement.preferredDefinition: An individual who uses a computer, program, network, or related service for work or entertainment. (from http://www.computeruser.com/resources/dictionary/index.html)_A secret set of characters, numbers, or symbols used as a form of authentication.:Coming after all others in time or space or degree or being the only one remaining.:The date and time at which an event occurs or occurred, computer generated but usually indicated in human-readable form, especially when used to track events._Generic value domain for a java SQL datatype that is a thin wrapper around java.util.Date that allows the JDBC API to identify this as a SQL TIMESTAMP value.
